window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This Christmas, I’m wishing for a present that money can’t buy….</b></p> <p>Aaron Townsend has given me a life beyond my wildest dreams. But not even a billionaire can prevent cancer.</p> <p>Now that I’m in remission, this Christmas I’d like a present that is priceless—spending time traveling with my five beautiful children and my husband by my side.</p> <p>But business never goes smoothly, and I don’t feel right sharing my request when Aaron has just discovered there’s a traitor in his ranks.</p> <p>There’s also another deal he’s keeping tight-lipped about, and I can tell it’s important. When our son requests to accompany his father on a business trip days before Christmas to close the deal, my heart sinks.</p> <p>Will Aaron make it home in time for the festive season? And am I silly to believe that he can make all of my Christmas wishes come true?</p>"; 
